{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Lead Orcs, Humans, Elves, or Demons in their quest to rule over Liria in this epic high-fantasy strategy RPG for 1-4 players.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now available:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc8e <strong>TUTORIAL</strong> \ud83d\udc8e </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc8e <strong>PVE</strong> \ud83d\udc8e </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc8e <strong>LOCAL MULTIPLAYER</strong> \ud83d\udc8e</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc8e <strong>Online MULTIPLAYER</strong> \ud83d\udc8e  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc8e <strong>CAMPAIGN</strong> \ud83d\udc8e </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Command Your Beloved Factions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose between <strong>Orcs</strong>, <strong>Humans</strong>, <strong>Elves</strong>, and <strong>Demons</strong> and use their unique abilities and play styles to <strong>seize control over Liria</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>HUMANS</strong>:\u00a0as <strong>Gregor the Mighty</strong>, the legendary fighter, you will inspire your army towards attack and throw yourself right in the middle of action.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>ORCS</strong>: As <strong>Bilar Crosschain</strong>, the Orc Shaman, you will tap into ancestral magic to sustain your army through battle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>ELVES</strong>: As <strong>Daria Nightshade</strong>, the arcane Elven sorceress, you will use your powers to protect your people and keep the woods of Numiria safe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>DEMONS</strong>: As <strong>Raegar</strong>, the Demon lord, you will manipulate the life and death points of your enemies and foes. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/Attack.gif?t=1738401621\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master Powerful Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fire Axe, Amulet of Fate, Shadow Shield and many others await you: collect treasure chests and fight monsters to uncover <strong>legendary weapons and artefacts</strong> your units can equip.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/Units.gif?t=1738401621\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Channel Ancestral Magic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take advantage of your commander's <strong>unique powers</strong> to inspire your units, protect them from harm, or cause destruction on your enemies. Advance your level and <strong>unlock additional abilities</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/Spells.gif?t=1738401621\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defeat Nasty Monsters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The beautiful land of Liria is infested by monstrous creatures: some more common than others \u2013 like Goblins and Lizards \u2013 and some rare, like Balthazar, an ancient fearsome dragon. Defeat them and collect <strong>gold, loot, and XP points</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/Monsters.gif?t=1738401621\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unleash Epic Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Liria is a shape-shifting land: every session plays on a <strong>different map</strong>, making every scenario unique and challenging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/Map.gif?t=1738401621\" /></p>","achievements":{"highligh